    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a <strong>Mexican jumping bean</strong> fixing to bring the long arm of the law to the disorderly vegetables of <strong>Cactusdale</strong>. Armed with your trusty revolver, will you lock up these nutritious varmints and become the town’s next sheriff?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SPIN YOUR GUN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/c73981644b769fbe54bbd44ff7bdfdf4.poster.avif?t=1765759378\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/c73981644b769fbe54bbd44ff7bdfdf4.webm?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/c73981644b769fbe54bbd44ff7bdfdf4.mp4?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master a unique shooting style where timing and positioning are essential for success. Rotate your gun clockwise or counterclockwise to shoot your way to survival!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PREPARE TO DIE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/97dfac14a2b492280248ec4f8b617c51.poster.avif?t=1765759378\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/97dfac14a2b492280248ec4f8b617c51.webm?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/97dfac14a2b492280248ec4f8b617c51.mp4?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How do you feel about dying over and over again? Each move must be quick and precise as you progress through different saloon rooms, as you are constantly outnumbered by a rogue’s gallery of wicked bandits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HEAT THE PLACE UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/495db1e1218226d6ef09bfdd1408c863.poster.avif?t=1765759378\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/495db1e1218226d6ef09bfdd1408c863.webm?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/495db1e1218226d6ef09bfdd1408c863.mp4?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop through the saloons of Cactusdale, taking down vegetable outlaws as quick as you can to rack up a bigger bounty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WIN THE DUELS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/b4561046a94da160ff4da654747cf2bc.poster.avif?t=1765759378\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/b4561046a94da160ff4da654747cf2bc.webm?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/b4561046a94da160ff4da654747cf2bc.mp4?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You might've died 20 times before you finally killed that boss, but isn't that the whole point of hardcore games?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE HOUSE ALWAYS WINS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/3038d38d23cfaa42caede062f137dd02.poster.avif?t=1765759378\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/3038d38d23cfaa42caede062f137dd02.webm?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207200/extras/3038d38d23cfaa42caede062f137dd02.mp4?t=1765759378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your hard-earned money in slot machines to get helpful upgrades or weapons. Sometimes it's a question of survival, so don't be ashamed!</p>",
